Package: autoSDM
Title: Species Distribution Modeling using Alpha Earth Embeddings
Version: 0.1.0
Author: James Longo [aut, cre]
Maintainer: James Longo <james.longo.birds@gmail.com>
Description: Facilitates Species Distribution Modeling (SDM) by leveraging Google's Alpha Earth satellite embeddings. The package provides tools for extracting high-resolution (10m) 64-dimensional dense vectors from Google Earth Engine (GEE), training niche centroid and machine learning models, and generating suitability maps. All computationally intensive tasks are performed server-side on GEE to ensure scalability for large datasets.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
